		<eng value="{W}{F-2002_10}{A-C}{S-O}{CB-255,255,255,255} If you want a combat-heavy challenge,{N}{S-S} try Deathmatch!{N}{N}{F-2002_10}{S-N}{A-L}{CB-166,166,166,255}Overview{N} In Deathmatch mode, you'll fight alongside your team against the enemy team."/>
