	<string key="1015">
		<eng value="{W}{F-2002_10}{A-C}{S-O}{CB-255,255,255,255} If you want to experience the thrill of sports,{N} try Touchdown!{N}{N}{F-2002_10}{S-N}{A-L}{CB-166,166,166,255} Overview{N} In Touchdown mode, you must protect your own goal, while taking the ball at the center of the map and carrying it to the enemy’s goal."/>
