	<string key="1017">
		<eng value="{W}{F-2002_10}{A-C}{S-O}{CB-255,255,255,255}Don't look now, but there's someone behind you! If you love the thrill of the chase,{N} try Chaser!{N}{N}{F-2002_10}{S-N}{A-L}{CB-166,166,166,255}* Overview{N} In Chaser mode, one player is a Chaser with enhanced powers. Other players must avoid the Chaser as much as possible."/>
